latestPosts.caption:
Story time. 📢 
Recently, I met a friend who told me that my profile looks more like a promotional page than a reflection of my life. That comment lingered. And the truth is that,he wasn’t wrong.

From January until now, I stopped posting. I hated the way I looked. I gained weight, and it discouraged me from taking pictures. My work continued, life moved forward, but I forgot something important: this is a part of my life too. The little weight I gained—I can lose it easily, if I want to. But more importantly, I let other people’s views of me affect how I viewed myself.

That’s why I stopped sharing my moments—my happy, personal, imperfect moments.
So here’s to changing that. ❤️

Here’s a photo dump of how my past five months went. Yup, the only photos I took, really. I’m shocked too
Anyway, Enjoy. And cheers to more. To showing up. To living all of it. #selflove #selfloveera #storytime #goa #lifestyleinfluencer

Goa is getting its first-ever state private university — Parul University Goa Campus!
Located just 500 meters from the beach, this 50,000 sqm campus blends modern architecture with nature, offering world-class programs in Engineering, Management, IT, Nursing, Pharmacy, and Health Sciences.
Special scholarships available for Goan students!
